data.description: Discover elegance in this charming brick residence nestled in the serene Hatridge Addition. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, this expansive home provides a comfortable and inviting living space. The inclusion of a 2-car garage adds both convenience and additional storage to meet your needs.  Upon entering, be captivated by the open concept design that seamlessly connects the kitchen, breakfast room, and dining room. This well-thought-out layout creates a delightful flow, ideal for hosting gatherings and entertaining loved ones. The kitchen is adorned with granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances, presenting a sleek and modern aesthetic.  The primary retreat is a true sanctuary, featuring double lavatories, a jetted tub, and a separate shower. An oasis awaits in the backyard—step onto the generous patio to bask in the outdoor space, whether for relaxation or hosting activities. The privacy fence surrounding the backyard ensures tranquility and seclusion, allowing you to fully appreciate your outdoor haven.  3701 Connie not only boasts visual appeal but also provides a practical and comfortable living environment. Don't miss the chance to claim this gem as your new home, conveniently located near schools, parks, shopping, and medical facilities. Your dream home awaits!
